# Local-only SECRETS for `astro dev` and `wrangler` (loaded by platformProxy).
#
# Setup:
#   1. Copy this file to `.dev.vars`   (that file is gitignored — never commit it)
#   2. Fill in the real values below
#
# Non-secret config (site name, contact email, from address) lives in
# wrangler.jsonc under "vars" — edit it there, not here.
#
# In PRODUCTION, set this secret with:  npx wrangler secret put RESEND_API_KEY
# (or via the Cloudflare dashboard → Worker → Settings → Variables).

RESEND_API_KEY=re_your_resend_api_key_here
